data.revised_prompt: Create a high-quality, photorealistic image of a 'Tropical Twister' cocktail, served in a clear stemmed hurricane glass. It contains layered colors, from deep amber of dark rum and Campari at the bottom, which fades into a golden hue at the top where the pineapple juice mixes. An inviting slice of pineapple sits on the rim, accompanied by a glossy maraschino cherry. The glass gleams under soft, warm lighting, sparking in subtle reflections. As a backdrop, there is an out-of-focus image of a sandy beach, further accentuating the exotic feel of the cocktail. The frame avoids text and watermarks and primarily focuses on the cocktail, capturing its vibrant essence against a tranquil, sun-dappled setting.
